ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent an environment type used to identify an ambulatory surgical center.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) category Encounter or attribute Admission Source. The intent of this data element is to identify an environment type that defines an ambulatory surgical center. ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with ambulatory surgical centers.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
